parties who contributed to the success of diplomacy, especially
Syria which showed its eagerness to reach this stage, and appeals
to the Syrian leadership to agree to negotiate through
international organizations to ensure success to the initiative.
   Lastly, the organization notes that the success of this
initiative could be an adequate introduction to curb the dramatic
developments of the hostages issue.
   Victory to the downtrodden in the march toward justice,
   Glory and immortality for our martyrs,
   The Revolutionary Justice Organization.
