<DATELINE>TUNIS, Tunisia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Yasser Arafat's Fatah movement adopted a
proposal Sunday to establish a Palestinian currency to be backed
with gold donated by PLO supporters, the Palestinian news agency
