<HEAD>Man Executed for Killing National Congress Member</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BEIJING (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man has been executed in southeastern China for
murdering a member of the National Congress last June, an official
newspaper reported Sunday.
   The Beijing Daily said Yuan Zihu was executed Saturday in Yongan
